title: Match history failing to load (out of client)
body:
The Oceania match history is not loading for me, when ever I go to it It's just this blank screen.
My friends are also having the same issue..
I have tried other browsers, I have cleared my cache and cookies and nothing is working.

However if i visit the NA match history it works fine.
Please help :D

{{champion:103}}
